TITLE: Implementing Non-blocking Data Fetching in Vue
DESCRIPTION: This snippet demonstrates how to implement lazy loaders for non-blocking data fetching. It uses the lazy option to allow navigation to proceed while data is being fetched, useful for non-critical data.
SOURCE: https://github.com/posva/unplugin-vue-router/blob/main/docs/data-loaders/rfc.md#2025-04-21_snippet_17

LANGUAGE: vue
