TITLE: Configuring DataLoaderPlugin with Navigation Result Selection in TypeScript
DESCRIPTION: This snippet shows how to configure the DataLoaderPlugin with a custom selectNavigationResult function to handle multiple navigation results from parallel data loaders, prioritizing specific navigation outcomes.
SOURCE: https://github.com/posva/unplugin-vue-router/blob/main/docs/data-loaders/rfc.md#2025-04-21_snippet_12

LANGUAGE: typescript
CODE:
```
app.use(DataLoaderPlugin, {
  router,
  selectNavigationResult(results) {
    for (const { value } of results) {
      if (
        typeof value === 'object' &&
        'name' in value &&
        value.name === 'not-found'
      ) {
        return value
      }
    }
  },
})
```

